.affiliate.description2:
1. Choose a banner below, fill in all information and the URL where you plan to put your banner (the banner will function anywhere, but it helps us to monitor activity). If you are using your own banner, linking directly to the products or just using a text link you can change the html after signing up. Please make sure your email address is entered correctly; the HTML code you need to add to your page is sent to your email address.

2. After you are done filling out the information required below, click on the sign-up button. The code you need to add to your page should arrive in your email within a few seconds. Make sure you do not alter the code in any way; changing it could result in someone else receiving credit for your sales. If you needed to change the code for any reason please contact us first.

3. The last step is to add the code to your webpage and upload your new page. Try clicking on the banner once to make sure it works.
.affiliate.description:
Sign up now and you will receive a $10.00 coupon in store credit towards anything on our site!

  • Our company offers one of the highest paying affiliate programs you will find. We pay 10% commissions on each sale generated. Commissions are paid at the end of each month as long as the commissions earned total over $50.00. If the commissions earned for a month do not equal $50.00 or more, the commissions earned will be carried over to the next month until the $50.00 commission minimum is earned.

  • By signing up you also may use our Two-Tier program which allows you to sign up affiliates underneath you to earn 2% commissions from sales they generate.


  • GKWorld will also supply banners, buttons and text links that you can put on your site to promote the affiliate program so you can make money. You can also put a picture of the product on your site and link directly to the product on our site.

premier of its newest character Yoshi. With bright red boots on his feet and an
ever present grin, this lovable egg hatched dinosaur grew to become Mario's
accomplice and friend. Together they braved the tricky and maze link Dinosaur
Land in search of Princess Peach and fellow dinosaur friends of Yoshi. Both had
been imprisoned by the evil spiked turtle, Bowers and his minions.

If your a fan of retro video games and video game collectible toys, surely a
===yoshi plush toy===
 will not disappoint. Super Mario World debuted in 1990 with the
premier of its newest character Yoshi. With bright red boots on his feet and an
ever present grin, this lovable egg hatched dinosaur grew to become Mario's
accomplice and friend. Together they braved the tricky and maze link Dinosaur
Land in search of Princess Peach and fellow dinosaur friends of Yoshi. Both had
been imprisoned by the evil spiked turtle, Bowers and his minions.
.genre.nintendomariobros.super_mario_bro.description:
With a technology new to NES and addictive storyline, Nintendo fans around the
globe were hooked and Yoshi, through his buoyant hop, mushroom snatching long
tongue and the spotted green eggs, became a memorable character.


This was only the beginning of Yoshi's appearance in video games and pop
culture. Whether blue, yellow or his trademarked lime green,Yoshi became a big
player at Nintendo with games like Super Mario Cart and even a tv show later
on.  Soon to follow was an awesome variety of merchandise like a

.skate.returns.description:
Return Policy:
If for any reason you receive an item damaged or broken you may send it back to us for a replacement of the same item only, all sales are final. We'll also pay the return shipping costs if the return is a result of our error (you received an incorrect or defective item, etc.).


If you have eligible products to return, you must contact us via our contact page within 30 days to obtain an RMA Number. Returns will not be accepted after 30 days from receipt of delivery or without a valid Return Merchandise Authorization (RMA) Number.


We'll notify you via e-mail of your refund once we've received and processed the returned item, and we'll issue a refund in the same form of payment originally used for the purchase within 3 to 5 business days of our receiving your return. If you paid by check, it will take longer for you to receive the refund.


If you wish to cancel a pre-order please contact us via our contact page, please note the 20% deposit is non-refundable.
Shipping Policy:
Our orders normally ship within 1-2 business days unless stated otherwise. The shipping cost for this item is determined by your location. Please enter your zip code in the shipping calculator to determine the shipping cost before bidding to avoid any confusion. If the shipping calculator does not display for you then please e-mail us for a shipping quote.


If you do not agree with the shipping & handling price, do not bid. Please do not argue the S&H fees after a bid is placed or product is delivered.


We do combine shipping for multiple items purchased. We calculate shipping by weight, small items are approximately only $1-$2 per additional item. For larger items and international orders, shipping may be more per item.


After your order is shipped you will receive the shipping confirmation for your order via e-mail.


Orders normally take 2-5 business days to arrive after they are shipped and you receive the shipping confirmation. International orders can take anywhere from 1-3 weeks to arrive after being shipped. We unfortunately cannot provide tracking numbers for international customers through USPS at this time unless EMS (express mail service) is purchased.

.shipping.shipping_policies.description_ret_right:
==Domestic Shipping:==
Shipments are sent from PA, USA. Priority Mail and Fed Ex Home Delivery usually take 1-5 business days to arrive from when you receive the shipping notice. Standard shipping usually arrives in 3-10 business days after being shipped.


==Domestic back ordered items:==
If you order in-stock items and back ordered items together we will in most cases ship the in-stock items to you within 1-2 days and the back ordered items separately. You will NOT be charged any additional shipping.



==International Shipping:==
Shipments by first class mail usually take around 1-3 weeks to arrive after they are shipped, pending customs and holidays it may take longer. Global Priority and Express Mail usually takes around 3-7 business days to arrive.


==International back ordered items:==
Orders shipping outside the USA with in-stock and back ordered items will be held until all items are available. In some cases we may ship the in-stock items to you early and the back ordered items separately. You will NOT be charged any additional shipping.


==International Duty & Customs Fees:==
GKWorld has no control over what countries charge to import merchandise. We charge the shipping it takes to get from us to your country, it is then out of our hands after that. Please check with customs in your country if concerned about any import fees.
.shipping.shipping_policies.description_ret_left:
==FREE SHIPPING on orders in the USA $75+==
(excludes Hawaii, Alaska, Puerto Rico and Guam)


==Items that display "Ships in 1-2 business days":==
These items are in-stock and ready to ship.


==How we determine shipping costs:==
Shipping costs are determined by the weight of the items ordered and where they are shipped to. On the shopping cart page you can enter your zip code to display the shipping costs. You can add/remove items to see how shipping costs change.


==Items that display "Back Order":==
These items are on back order and usually re-stock within 1-3 weeks from when they are ordered but in some cases may take longer. Back orders can be cancelled at anytime.
